Retrieves details of 1 record from an app.




Parameter








Name


Type


Required


Description










app


Integer


yes


The kintone app ID






id


Integer


yes


The record ID in kintone app








Return


Promise


Sample code




Get record


 Source code 


let app = /*{your_app_id}*/;
let id = {your_record_id};
kintoneRecord.getRecord(app, id)
